Definition: a meeting of the eyes between two people that expresses meaningful nonverbal communication
Example: it was a mere glance, but the eye contact was enough to tell her that he was desperate to leave
Synonyms: visual_communication, a, meeting, of, the, eyes, between, two, people, that, expresses, meaningful, nonverbal, communication, it, was, mere, glance, but, eye, contact, enough, to, tell, her, he, desperate, leave
Category: noun.communication
